description.narrative: This activity (Fleet Management support to Districts) is a component of Maintaining Resilient Zero for Ebola in Sierra Leone reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £7,400,578. This component benefits Sierra Leone, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Infectious disease control. , with the following implementing partners: International Procurement Agency. The start date is 01-04-2016 and the end date is 31-12-2017.
